text: The Swan 86 was a boat designed by German Frers, built by Nautor's Swan and first launched in 1988. It is unusual for swan featuring a keel similar in plan form to 12 metre Australia II. ==External links== * Nautor Swan * German Frers Official Website ==References== Category:Sailing yachts Category:Keelboats Category:1980s sailboat type designs Category:Sailboat types built by Nautor Swan Category:Sailboat type designs by Germán Frers
